[{"_path":"/legacy-articles/2020-09-01-12th-ithome-ironman","_dir":"legacy-articles","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"第 12 屆 iT 邦幫忙鐵人賽","description":"","excerpt":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ithelp.ithome.com.tw/2020-12th-ironman","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第 12 屆 iT 邦幫忙鐵人賽"}]},{"type":"text","value":"在今天開賽了。這是我第 4 次參加鐵人賽。今年有三個不一樣的地方："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"其一，是我第一次參加團體組，和同事一起以「"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ithelp.ithome.com.tw/2020-12th-ironman/signup/team/126","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"威士忌打字機"}]},{"type":"text","value":"」的隊名參賽。不過我可沒有能耐每次寫文都喝一杯威士忌呀。這可是由 2 個 Scrum Master、1 個工程師加上一個曾經當過 PO 的豪華組合呀！歡迎大家多多關注。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"其二，是我終於不是多個主題一起開賽，有別於以往一次兩到三個主題一起寫，讓自己陷入修羅，今年決定和平一點，每七天決定是否多開一個主題。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"其三，是我竟然為系列文寫綱要了！這和過往每天在寫題目的做法截然不同。究竟我為什麼有這個改變，以及我怎麼擬綱要，就往下閱讀下去吧！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"今天開始了我的第一個主題系列文"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ithelp.ithome.com.tw/users/20103676/ironman/3446","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《為自己學習成為 Scrum Master 的經驗分享》"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。主要是講述我進兩年半成為 Scrum Master 的學習歷程，會用淺白的文字、說故事的語氣，和大家聊聊這段過去經歷過的事情、閱讀過的好書、參加過的聚會的等等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"若是在七天後我又多開了一個主題，再讓我更新這篇文章讓大家知道吧～"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在這篇文章也記錄這次書寫的方式。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我這次使用了 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://miro.com/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Miro"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 協助我制定系列文的大綱。與其說是大綱，不如說是關鍵字。我先建立了 30 張空白黃色便利貼用來寫關鍵字，看著題目去思考我想寫些什麼，每一概念就寫填寫一張便利貼，然後我也可以知道我還剩幾張便利貼要寫關鍵字。編寫可能就順便為一些關鍵字用藍色便利貼建立一個群組，這個群組可能是分類、或是時期、或是更概括的觀念。有了群組後，我也可以透過群組得到更多發想去寫可能原本沒想到的關鍵字。然後逐漸把 30 張黃色便利貼寫滿，我這個主題的綱要就完成囉！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"12th-Ironman-Template.jpg","src":"12th-Ironman-Template.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n用便利貼寫關鍵字去組成大綱，這裡是用 Miro 去實踐"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這樣做的好處就是我是用發散的方式去想我要寫什麼，而不會一開始就被架構給束縛著我的想法。而且隨時方便調整，不一定要按照這樣的綱要去寫，隨時可以增減關鍵字，甚至寫一些額外的關鍵字，也可以在該個關鍵字寫起來內容太多時去拆分。當了兩年多的 Scrum Master，我的腦袋都成了便利貼的形狀了呢～"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"另外，有別於過去幾年使用 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://bear.app/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bear App"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 去書寫文章，我這次改用在"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://blog.starrocket.io/posts/category/podcast/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"星箭廣播 Podcast"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 常被提到的 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ulysses.app/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ulysses"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 作為邊寫工具。其實去年在寫文就有嘗試過，但後來還是放棄。會有這樣的改變主要是我有在訂閱的 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://blog.starrocket.io/posts/setapp-is-a-netflix-for-mac-apps-service-create-a-triple-wins-for-developers-consumers-and-itself/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"App 界 Netflix"}]},{"type":"text","value":"——"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://setapp.com/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Setapp"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 服務裡面有，而且也推出 iOS 可以使用的模式。介面似乎也改版過，變得比較合我胃口，所以就想說來用它來寫文章。當然，更重要的是，他也是基於 Markdown 語法的文字編輯器囉！不然可能連考慮都不考慮了，哈。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"CleanShot-2020-09-03-at-23.41.02.png","src":"CleanShot-2020-09-03-at-23.41.02.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n這是 Ulysses 的介面，簡潔實用"}]}]},"title_en":"12th iThome Ironman","slug":"12th-ithome-ironman","aliases":["第 12 屆 iT 邦幫忙鐵人賽","12th iThome Ironman"],"created_at":"2020-09-01T22:41:46.000Z","published_at":null,"updated_at":null,"tags":[],"moc":["Announcement"],"_type":"markdown","_id":"garden:legacy-articles:2020-09-01-12th-ithome-ironman.md","_source":"garden","_file":"legacy-articles/2020-09-01-12th-ithome-ironman.md","_extension":"md"},{"_path":"/legacy-articles/2021-03-14-timers-to-avoid-digressing-for-too-long","_dir":"legacy-articles","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"避免跑題太久的計時器","description":"","excerpt":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在引導團隊進行 Retrospective 時，難免會遇到有些團隊思維比較跳躍，容易在對話進行中跑題、聊開。直接制止難免會掃興，讓對話氣氛凝滯；但放任又難免導致時間延宕，無法準時結束這場對話。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我最近在處理引導這類團隊的對話時，會帶著一個 8 寸以上的 Time Timer，將這個 Timer 交給對話圈中，坐在我對面的夥伴。然後向團隊說，如果發現團隊開始跑題時，就請這位夥伴幫我們撥個一分鐘計時。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"當團隊看到這位夥伴撥動 Timer 時，就會意識到自己跑題了，然後就會開始有意識地收斂回來。就算來不及收斂，當 Timer 響了，我們也會遵守這樣的默契，回到對話的正軌上。"}]}]},"title_en":"Timers to avoid digressing for too long","slug":"timers-to-avoid-digressing-for-too-long","aliases":["避免跑題太久的計時器","Timers to avoid digressing for too long"],"created_at":"2021-03-14T23:21:31.000Z","published_at":null,"updated_at":null,"tags":[],"moc":["Agile"],"_type":"markdown","_id":"garden:legacy-articles:2021-03-14-timers-to-avoid-digressing-for-too-long.md","_source":"garden","_file":"legacy-articles/2021-03-14-timers-to-avoid-digressing-for-too-long.md","_extension":"md"}]